<body><div class="game-shell"><div class="top-bar"><div class="title-block"><h1>Crypto Clicker</h1><span>Click for crypto!</span></div><div class="nav-buttons"><button class="nav-btn" id="openAscension"><span class="icon">⬆</span>Ascension</button><button class="nav-btn secondary" id="openWorlds"><span class="icon">🌍</span>Worlds</button><button class="nav-btn" id="openUtilities"><span class="icon">⚙</span>Utilities</button></div></div><div class="main-grid"><div class="panel"><div class="panel-inner"><div class="panel-header"><h2>Crypto</h2><span id="currentWorldLabel">Green World</span></div><div class="crypto-display"><div class="world-label" id="worldLabelSmall">Green World</div><div class="crypto-count" id="cryptoCount">0</div><div class="crypto-per-sec" id="cryptoPerSec">0 / sec</div><div class="crypto-coin" id="cryptoCoin"></div></div></div></div><div class="panel"><div class="panel-inner"><div class="panel-header"><h2>Upgrades</h2><span>Boost your earnings</span></div><div class="upgrades-list" id="upgradesList"></div></div></div></div><div class="panel"><div class="panel-inner"><div class="panel-header"><h2>Status</h2><span>Game Stats</span></div><div class="status-bar"><div class="status-pill">World: <strong id="statusWorld">Green</strong></div><div class="status-pill">Ascensions: <strong id="statusAscensions">0</strong></div><div class="status-pill">Total Crypto: <strong id="statusTotalCrypto">0</strong></div><div class="status-pill danger">Resets: <strong id="statusResets">0</strong></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="overlay" id="ascensionOverlay"><div class="overlay-inner"><div class="overlay-content"><div class="overlay-header"><h2>Ascension</h2><button class="overlay-close" id="closeAscension">✕</button></div><div class="ascension-center"><div class="ascension-count">You have <strong id="ascensionCount">0</strong> ascensions</div><div class="rainbow-crypto" id="ascendButton"><div class="rainbow-crypto-inner"></div></div><div class="ascension-warning">Ascension resets ALL progress.<br>Requires Timer Miner upgrade.</div><div class="ascension-message" id="ascensionMessage"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="overlay" id="worldsOverlay"><div class="overlay-inner"><div class="overlay-content"><div class="overlay-header"><h2>Worlds</h2><button class="overlay-close" id="closeWorlds">✕</button></div><div class="worlds-grid"><div class="world-card"><div class="world-main"><div class="world-name">Green World</div><div class="world-status">Status: <span class="unlocked">Unlocked</span></div></div><div class="world-pill">Green</div><button class="world-select-btn" id="selectGreenWorld">Enter</button></div><div class="world-card"><div class="world-main"><div class="world-name">Purple World</div><div class="world-status">Status: <span class="locked">Locked</span> (Requires 2 Ascensions)</div></div><div class="world-pill purple">Purple</div><button class="world-select-btn" id="selectPurpleWorld" disabled>Enter</button></div></div></div></div></div>
